# GitHub remote (SSH)

For this repository, treat **`git@github.com:kmabery/pipeline-eval.git`** as the canonical clone/push URL. Prefer **SSH** for Git fetch/push from agents and docs; confirm with `git remote -v` in the workspace.

**Default branch for handoffs:** **`main`** unless your pipeline or workflow explicitly builds another branch.

Do **not** store private keys, PATs, or `gh` tokens in the repository. See [Connecting to GitHub with SSH](https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/connecting-to-github-with-ssh).
